    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a reliable foundation for a driver who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dings, some paint chips on the hood, and clear coat fading on the roof and trunk. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and staining from regular use. While it runs and drives, it will likely need some minor suspension work and a fresh set of tires in the near future to be in top shape. It's a solid, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a dependable commuter.",
