      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this fantastic fixer-upper opportunity! While this vehicle has definitely seen better days and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it remains a great project for a dedicated hobbyist or anyone looking for a budget-friendly way to get a specific model. It's an honest car that needs a lot of love, but it's ready for its next chapter with a new owner who sees its hidden potential!",
      "price": 5500.0,
